Carlotta Freeman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlotta_Freeman 0 Carlotta Freeman (c.1877–June 11, 1954) was an American stage actress. She was one of the first African American women in the legitimate theatre. Carlotta_Freeman ( c. 1877 – June_11_,_1954 ) was an_American_stage_actress . She was one of the_first_African_American_women in the_legitimate_theatre .
